* Task 3 fixture: CALLNAT dynamic extraction (FR-11, FR-17, M-6)
* Contains one variable-target call (#PROGNAME) and one literal call ('STATIC')
* to prove static and dynamic edges coexist and are visibly distinct in one file.
* Neither call should produce a diagnostic — the variable target is a modeled outcome, not an error.

DEFINE DATA
LOCAL
  1 PROGNAME (A30)
END DEFINE

CALLNAT #PROGNAME

CALLNAT 'STATIC'

MOVE 'DONE' TO PROGNAME

END
